    <br>
    <h2 style="color:#97bf0d;text-align:center;">Create your holiday in the beautiful coast of the Po Delta Park Riviera with just a few clicks!</h2>
    <div style="text-align:center;"><img src="/immagini/guida.png" alt="" width="150" /></div>
<h3 style="color:#0087cc;text-align:center;">You can choose one of the <strong>already created packages</strong> that include stay and entertainments to live an extraordinary holiday. </h3>
    <div style="text-align:center;"><img src="/immagini/trip.png" width="150" alt="" /></div>
    <h3 style="color:#0087cc;text-align:center;">Or you can create your <strong>own packages</strong>, by choosing among loads of stay opportunities and among the most beautiful cultural and naturalistic activities to do during your holiday. </h3>
    <hr />
    <p>Your booking will be managed by <strong>Po Delta Tourism</strong>, the main touristic agency in the Po Delta Park Riviera. The stay and the activities will take place at the affiliated facilities.</p>
    <br>
    <h2 style="color:#97bf0d;text-align:center;"> The advantages?</h2>
    <img src="immagini/help.png" width="70" alt="" style="float:left; margin-right:20px;" />
    <p><strong>SAFE HOLIDAY ASSISTANCE: </strong>for every need before, during and after your holiday you can contact us through the site form or via email, or you can call us at +390533776100.</p>
    <br>
    <img src="immagini/discount.png" width="70" alt="" style="float:left; margin-right:20px;" />
    <p><strong>BEST PRICE GUARANTEED: </strong>thanks to our agreement with most of the touristic facilities on the coast we can guarantee you complete packages at a discounted price. </p>
